last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 10
last_episode_to_air.overview: Players turn into barnyard snacks. A whip-cracking challenge sets off a milk shower. A buzz saw party becomes a true buzzkill.

name: Flinch
overview: Harrowing and hilarious tests await the brave and foolhardy, as well as the judges, in this comedy game show. If they flinch, they feel the pain.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Contestants go for a dizzying dip. Target practice takes an electrifying turn. A train carrying special cargo causes a big stink.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Popping balloons, swinging tires and a chicken-feeding frenzy separate the flinchers from the fearless. Fireworks put a judge in a painful position.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Jack-in-the-boxes, a flying washing machine and emus receive mixed reactions. The losing judge takes in a big whiff of filth.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Players feel the burn with hot wax. Later, they dive into a bed of mousetraps, and gags abound when a train reeking of rot rolls through.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Loud noises lead to massive wedgies, while close encounters with rats set off mousetraps. A balloon-popping challenge gets dumped on one judge.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: A little boy and a jack-in-the-box give a shocking performance. Contestants get caked with flour. A big bang means a dirty bath.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Chainsaws, a spinning wheel and a pecking chicken party rattle contestants' composures. Tasting sweet misery, a judge gets a face full of pie.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Contestants get the boot in a hog-wild challenge before learning that fireworks and rubber bands don't mix. Later, they try to extinguish their fears.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Terror comes in the form of a flying barrel, zaps from a brass band and a slap-happy challenge involving a weasel.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Players turn into barnyard snacks. A whip-cracking challenge sets off a milk shower. A buzz saw party becomes a true buzzkill.
